      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 SQA documentation was reviewed and confirmed current. All case files, UDFs, and post-processing scripts are stored in a Git repository with tagged releases corresponding to each simulation campaign. Gradation 2 requirements are fully satisfied."
