        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Discretization error acceptance criteria — MRL 2",
        "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% on primary QoI (relative hemolysis index and pressure head) using at least three systematically refined meshes with refinement ratio ≥ 1.3."
      },
      "rationale": "Three meshes (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.2 M cells) were generated with a uniform refinement ratio of 1.38. GCI for RH index = 2.1%; GCI for pressure head = 1.4%. Both are below the 5% threshold. Asymptotic range confirmed (GCI ratio = 0.98)."
