        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Output comparison acceptance criteria — MRL 2",
        "description": "Simulated RH index must agree with experimental RH index within ±15% at all five operating points; pressure head within ±10%."
      },
      "rationale": "Simulated RH index agreed with experimental measurements within 9.3% (max) across all five operating points. Pressure head agreement was within 6.1% (max). Both QoIs satisfy acceptance thresholds. Worst-case operating point (5 L/min, 3500 RPM) correctly identified by simulation."
    },
    {
