      "rationale": "Use error assessment is not required at MRL 2 for a Class II CPB device per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The simulation workflow is executed by trained CFD engineers following a documented standard operating procedure; formal use-error analysis is deferred to MRL 3+ submissions."
