      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2. Key inputs (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions) are documented and their sources traceable to calibrated measurements. A sensitivity sweep over ±5% inlet velocity and ±3% viscosity was performed informally and showed < 8% variation in RH index, supporting adequacy of the nominal inputs."
